au.com.cybersearch2.classynode

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.com.cybersearch2.classynode.NodeEntity
      • au.com.cybersearch2.classynode.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Node
extends NodeEntity
    Node Anchor for a component of a graph. Each node has a model which identifies what the node contains. The top node of a graph has a special model called "root".
    Author:
    Andrew Bowley 05/09/2014
    See Also:

        public static Node marshall(NodeEntity nodeEntity)
